### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### ICEPLAY API — Test Requests
### How to use: click "Send Request" above any request
### Change @baseUrl to your Railway URL when testing production
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api
@adminEmail = super@fropen.com
@adminPassword = admin123

### ─── 1. REGISTER a new user ─────────────
# @name register
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### ─── 2. LOGIN with admin user ────────────
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

### ─── 3. LOGIN with registered user ───────
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### ─── 4. REGISTER — missing fields (expect 400 error) ───
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "incomplete@example.com"
}

### ─── 5. REGISTER — short password (expect 400 error) ───
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Short Pass",
  "email": "shortpass@example.com",
  "password": "123"
}

### ─── 6. GET teams (protected — needs Bearer token) ─────
### Paste the token from login response below after "Bearer "
GET {{baseUrl}}/teams
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### ─── 7. GET players (protected) ────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/players
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### ─── 8. GET championships (protected) ──────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/championships
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
